## 💰 The pricing philosophy

Pricing reinforces positioning. VIRL's pricing supports the strategist category.

### Current pricing structure

**Founder Circle (first 50 paying customers):** $20/mo or $215/yr for life as long as continuously subscribed, plus perks. Closed when full.
**Standard:** $25/mo or $249/yr.

### Pricing reasoning

**$25/mo Standard is strategically positioned.** High enough to signal we're not a commodity AI generator (those cluster at $10-20). Accessible enough to be a "yes" for solo operators (vs $500/mo agencies). Establishes us as the premium tool in the AI category while remaining the accessible alternative in the strategist category.

**Founder Circle is intentionally a single tier.** "First 50 get $20 for life" is sharper than tiered structures. Cleaner story, simpler operations, concentrated scarcity, bounded margin exposure.

### Future pricing roadmap

**Pro tier ($39-49/mo) — post-launch month 3-4:** Adds advanced strategist features (Sunday Review, unlimited trend integration, advanced format diversity). Strengthens strategist positioning.

**Studio tier ($99/mo) — Year 2:** Adds Direct Publishing, Multi-Brand workspaces, Voice Cloning. Approaches Social Media OS lane without abandoning strategist positioning.

### What we won't do

- ❌ Lower prices to compete with AI generators. Repositions us into the wrong category.
- ❌ Offer a permanent free tier. The 14-day trial is sufficient. Permanent free signals wrong audience.
- ❌ Discount aggressively. Founder Circle is the exception, not the rule.

